ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectEuropean Union on Security Procedures for Exchanging and Protecting Classified Information ** Agreement **
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to BRING INTO FORCE for Canada the AGREEMENT between the Government of Canada and the EUROPEAN UNION on SECURITY PROCEDURES FOR EXCHANGING AND PROTECTING CLASSIFIED INFORMATION.
